{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/ubz2zg","result":{"data":{"sitePage":null},"pageContext":{"url":"posts/ubz2zg","relativePath":"posts/ubz2zg","frontmatter":{"title":"Free Arch: 将React 井字棋搬到微信小程序之二","stackbit_url_path":"posts/ubz2zg","date":"2022-01-02T13:19:58","excerpt":"","tags":[],"categories":[],"template":"post"},"html":"<p>在前几天，我宣称通过少量开发，通过 react view 可以在一定程度上打破微信个人版小程序不能使用 web view 的限制。并展示了一个基本的例子，即将 react 官方的经典教程井字棋游戏搬到了微信小程序。</p>\n<p>有人看了就纳闷，那只是展示了一个九宫格呀，点击也没反应。</p>\n<p>这说明他没认真学习 react 官方的井字棋教程。该教程的初始状态就是如此，点不动的，在 code pen 也是这样。</p>\n<p>通过利用上一篇介绍的 babel as a service，今天不写任何代码，直接把 react 官方教程的井字棋游戏的终态也搬到小程序上，以移除读者们对这个 react view 的疑虑。</p>\n<p>终态是可以两个人互动的版本，要将终态也移到小程序，只需要把终态对应的 code pen 里的 js 文件粘贴到 replit ，预览没有任何问题后，把小程序读取初始态的url 换成新的终态的 url 即可。</p>\n<p>最终效果如下：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/jpeg/221736/1641134972096-12831e88-3bfb-4cc8-a96a-b3cd7334004e.jpeg#clientId=u82014b6d-fe57-4&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=1&#x26;crop=1&#x26;from=ui&#x26;id=ube9eb488&#x26;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&#x26;name=E01C612B-4B7F-440B-AFAE-D3D92087A570.jpeg&#x26;originHeight=430&#x26;originWidth=430&#x26;originalType=binary%E2%88%B6=1&#x26;rotation=0&#x26;showTitle=false&#x26;size=114651&#x26;status=done&#x26;style=none&#x26;taskId=ub0fc1a82-c098-450d-b94b-604ef6146fa&#x26;title=\" alt=\"E01C612B-4B7F-440B-AFAE-D3D92087A570.jpeg\"></p>","pages":[],"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jeff Tian","description":"A wild full stack developer","palette":"yellow","header":{"title":"Jeff Tian","tagline":"A wild developer","logo_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7z1ua3nTOC5B7DwwzAki8I/4e1a05f8db770c285a492eeb1eaa398f/imageedit_3_2509022194.png","background_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7m0jrKYaDBwEvlc5lo8nt6/6d50a5050d9cdc0d4d2047e35feac292/10648733_696750647079056_2800539603462658695_o.jpg","has_nav":true,"nav_links":[{"label":"Home","url":"/","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"About",